profile.name: Inventory Single Record - Default Create Instance
profile.description: Triggered by an action in Inventory, this job profile imports a single record from an external system, to create an Instance and MARC record

profile.name: Inventory Single Record - Default Update Instance
profile.description: Triggered by an action in Inventory, this job profile imports a single record from an external system, to update an existing Instance, and either create a new MARC record or update an existing MARC record

profile.name: Default - Create instance and SRS MARC Bib
profile.description: This job profile creates SRS MARC Bib records and corresponding Inventory Instances using the library's default MARC-to-Instance mapping. It can be edited, duplicated, or deleted.

profile.name: quickMARC Derive - Create SRS MARC Bib and Instance
profile.description: This job profile is used by the quickMARC Derive action to create a new SRS MARC Bib record and corresponding Inventory Instance. It cannot be edited or deleted.
